This paper deals with a bandit problem, which is a classic problem in machine learning and optimization. The paper also mentions that the problem can model online auctions, which falls under game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
